<item>
            <title>[TIKA-886] OOXMLExtractorFactory can leave files open</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-886</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As identified in an Alfresco bug (ALF-13106), OOXMLExtractorFactory doesn&apos;t currently allow the closing of OPCPackage instances created from Files. This is because the OPCPackage isn&apos;t associated with the TikaInputStream, so the close doesn&apos;t propogate&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12548505">TIKA-886</key>
            <summary>OOXMLExtractorFactory can leave files open</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
